				<td colspan="2"><span>Honestly.. I've never seen him heal himself to any degree that would be noticeable, stuns and blasts interrupting are more effective than manadrain though. Use your time / twist to increase the dps instead of manadraining during battle. 
<br />
Ary is leashed to his room.. you can split pull as a bard everything out of that room except the left back mob which is mezzable though. Drag him into the corner and whoop him down, the toughest part of that tower is the first chamber room really with that geranomoa elemental that spawns adds. I pulled that whole room alone and it was a lot of work but it CAN be done, .. died a couple of times but being hit by 4 mobs for over 1200 each hit is a lil uncomfortable heh. 
<br />
I probably wouldn't try Ary with one group at this point because he has so many HP that the battle would take so long you'd start having to deal with repops, the tower itself would be really difficult to do with 1 group I typically avoid that one for xp. All the others have nice crawl space but Ary's tower is a dangerous place for just one small group. </span></td>
